- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also likely as the paper focuses on interconnection networks and their properties. 
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) is a possible category as the paper discusses the design of interconnection networks for supercomputers. 
- cs.SI (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses the performance enhancement of interconnection networks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new routing algorithm for improved performance of interconnection networks.
